title: Home - 616c616e
text:
Hello there! Welcome to my personal blog, where I (will) post cool stuff I find, my opinions and thoughts, and some stuff that interests me. I’ll also try to create interactive lessons from an intuitive standpoint for mathematics and physics. With my belief in free and open-source, all of the contents on this website are licensed under the MIT license unless otherwise stated.
There’s currently not a lot on here, as I’ve recently started building this page.
Someone help me commit to doing these

A new ZKP authentication algorithm that is proof of work
This blog!
Edit wikipedia pages
Read research papers
